OL,3,CBBC apologises to Amanda Abbington and
OL,4,Cupholds 'some Strictly complaints'
OL,6,FActor Amanda Abbington has received an
OL,7,Fapology from the BBC, ITV News
OL,8,FEntertainment Reporter Rishi Davda has
OL,9,Fthe latest
OL,11,FThe BBC has apologised to former
OL,12,FStrictly Come Dancing contestant
OL,13,FAmanda Abbington following a report
OL,14,Finto the behaviour of her 2023 partner
OL,15,FGiovanni Pernice.
OL,17,FThe broadcaster says it had assessed
OL,18,Fand upheld "some, but not all, of the
OL,19,Fcomplaints made".
