OL,3,CBBC apologises to Amanda Abbington and
OL,4,Cupholds 'some Strictly complaints'
OL,6,FIn a statement, it said: "The BBC has
OL,7,Fnow concluded its review into the
OL,8,Fcomplaints made by Amanda Abbington
OL,9,Fagainst Giovanni Pernice. We take any
OL,10,Fallegations of bullying and harassment
OL,11,Fvery seriously and this review has
OL,12,Ftaken time due to its complex nature
OL,13,Fand our desire to ensure a rigorous
OL,14,Fand robust process was undertaken.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
