OL,3,CBBC apologises to Amanda Abbington and
OL,4,Cupholds 'some Strictly complaints'
OL,6,F"Strictly Come Dancing is a family
OL,7,Fshow and we rightly expect very high
OL,8,Fstandards. While competition can be
OL,9,Ftough, rigorous and demanding, we want
OL,10,Fthe show to ultimately be a joyous and
OL,11,Ftransformative experience. It is a
OL,12,Fgreat shame if this hasn't been the
OL,13,Fcase for everyone who has appeared on
OL,14,Fthe show.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
