OL,3,CBBC apologises to Amanda Abbington and
OL,4,Cupholds 'some Strictly complaints'
OL,6,F"We have assessed the complaints and
OL,7,Fwe have upheld some, but not all, of
OL,8,Fthe complaints made. We want to
OL,9,Fapologise to Amanda Abbington and to
OL,10,Fthank her for coming forward and
OL,11,Ftaking part. We know this would not
OL,12,Fhave been an easy thing to do."
OL,14,FThere were no findings relating to
OL,15,Fphysical aggression, but complaints of
OL,16,Fverbal bullying and harassment were
OL,17,Fupheld, the PA news agency understands.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
