OL,3,CBBC apologises to Amanda Abbington and
OL,4,Cupholds 'some Strictly complaints'
OL,6,FAbbington responded in a statement,
OL,7,Fsaying: "As the BBC has indicated
OL,8,Ftoday in its statement, my decision to
OL,9,Fcome forward and complain about
OL,10,FGiovanni Pernice's conduct towards me
OL,11,Fwas not an easy thing to do.
OL,13,F"In the days, weeks and months since I
OL,14,Fcontacted the BBC, I've been accused
OL,15,Fof being a liar, a troublemaker and of
OL,16,Fbeing "mad and unstable".
