OL,3,CBBC apologises to Amanda Abbington and
OL,4,Cupholds 'some Strictly complaints'
OL,6,F"I've also received rape and murder
OL,7,Fthreats and a bomb threat was sent to
OL,8,Fmy place of work. My family and
OL,9,Fchildren have also been subjected to
OL,10,Fthreats and intimidation.
OL,12,F"Despite this vile abuse, I've never
OL,13,Fregretted coming forward, and today's
OL,14,Fapology from the BBC is a vindication
OL,15,Fof my complaint.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
