OL,3,CBBC apologises to Amanda Abbington and
OL,4,Cupholds 'some Strictly complaints'
OL,6,F"It's not just a vindication for me,
OL,7,Fit's a vindication for the other
OL,8,Fpeople who have contacted me since I
OL,9,Fmade my complaint to express concerns
OL,10,Fabout their own experiences on
OL,11,FStrictly Come Dancing.
OL,13,F"I hope those who have felt unable to
OL,14,Fspeak out now will be more confident
OL,15,Fthat they will be listened to and
OL,16,Fbelieved.
OL,18,F"The BBC has invited me to meet with
OL,19,Fsenior management and this is
OL,20,Fsomething I will now be considering.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
