OL,3,CBBC apologises to Amanda Abbington and
OL,4,Cupholds 'some Strictly complaints'
OL,6,F"This apology means a great deal to
OL,7,Fme. So too does the fact that the BBC
OL,8,Fhave acknowledged the steps that were
OL,9,Fput in place to support and protect me
OL,10,Fand past contestants were "not enough".
OL,12,F"What matters most now is that lessons
OL,13,Fhave been learned and that the BBC
OL,14,Fmakes the changes they've promised, to
OL,15,Fensure others don't experience the
OL,16,Fsame ordeal that I and others like me
OL,17,Fdid."
