OL,3,CBBC apologises to Amanda Abbington and
OL,4,Cupholds 'some Strictly complaints'
OL,6,FIn a written statement, a spokesperson
OL,7,Ffor Giovanni Pernice said: "We are
OL,8,Fpleased that this six-month review has
OL,9,Fnot found any evidence of threatening
OL,10,For abusive behaviour by Giovanni.
OL,12,F"Giovanni is relieved that the
OL,13,Foverwhelming majority of allegations
OL,14,Fout to the BBC have not been upheld
OL,15,Fand looks forward to continuing his
OL,16,Fwork on Dancing With The Stars in
OL,17,FItaly this season."
