OL,3,CBBC apologises to Amanda Abbington and
OL,4,Cupholds 'some Strictly complaints'
OL,6,FAbbington left Strictly in October
OL,7,F2023 after five weeks' worth of shows,
OL,8,Fwith the BBC at the time saying she
OL,9,Fhad pulled out of the most recent
OL,10,Fperformance because of "medical
OL,11,Freasons". She then said her departure
OL,12,Fwas because of "personal reasons".
