OL,3,CBBC apologises to Amanda Abbington and
OL,4,Cupholds 'some Strictly complaints'
OL,6,FAbbington said in July she "would not
OL,7,Fhave been able to live with myself" if
OL,8,Fshe had stayed silent about her
OL,9,Fexperience.
OL,11,FAnother professional dancer, Graziano
OL,12,FDi Prima, then also left the show
OL,13,Fafter admitting to kicking his
OL,14,Fcelebrity partner Zara McDermott once
OL,15,Fduring rehearsals last year.
