OL,3,CBBC apologises to Amanda Abbington and
OL,4,Cupholds 'some Strictly complaints'
OL,6,FThe dancer's spokesperson Mark
OL,7,FBorkowski said that Di Prima "deeply
OL,8,Fregrets" an "isolated incident"
OL,9,Finvolving himself and McDermott,
OL,10,Fadding that he had been left "in a
OL,11,Fvery vulnerable state".
OL,13,FFollowing the string of complaints,
OL,14,Fthe BBC announced that contestants on
OL,15,FStrictly Come Dancing will now be
OL,16,Fsupervised "at all times" by a
OL,17,Fproduction team member, including
OL,18,Fduring rehearsals.
